<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>447</hymn_number>
<author>Chinlang</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mihing hi bang ahim Lalmang?
 Na cha van apat Na hun sawl?
 Na hehpihna thuk leh sanzie, Lalmang,
 Mihing pilnan sutdawk zolo!

[V2]
 Gel maw'ng e, Gel maw'ng e, Gel maw'ng,
 Mihing leh Na hehpih thimthu;
 Mihing pilna'n sutdawk zolo, Lalmang,
 Lauthan lunglai ah hun gen hen!

[V3]
 2. Mihing hi bang ahim Lalpa?
 Van chutphah nusien Na hung tan;
 Na hehpihna thuk zie sanzie, Lalpa,
 Sietlei hingmi'n sutdawk zolo!

[V4]
 3. Mihing hi bang ahim Lalmang?
 Kum sang zatam Na lunggimna;
 &quot;A gawl thân, a lei thepna&quot; hilo maw?,
 Nau bang Na dawpna a sang hi?

[V5]
 4. Mihing hi bang ahim Lalmang?
 Van-go luoh din ngaihkhuo na tuoh;
 Hehpihna sang, panpihna sang, Lalmang,
 Mihing thimthu zaila'n lel mawh.</lyrics>
<title>WHAT IS MAN?</title>
</song>